Normally, when runnging a SLAM Algorithm, the Create3 processor is overlaoded and stops moving at some point. Use the republisher to solve the problem. Note, this solution worked for Raspberry Pi 4, it still has to be proved for Raspberry Pi 5, but there is no hint, it wont work.
<br>https://github.com/iRobotEducation/create3_examples/blob/humble/create3_republisher/README.md</br>
